'''巴魯卡里難民營'''是[[孟加拉国|孟加拉国]][[吉大港專區|吉大港專區]][[科克斯巴扎爾|科克斯巴扎爾]]的一個[[罗兴亚人|罗兴亚]][[难民营|难民营]]。<ref name="theguardianaidreachesrohingya">{{cite news|title=Aid reaches Rohingya refugees in Bangladesh – in pictures|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/gallery/2017/feb/17/aid-reaches-rohingya-refugees-in-bangladesh-in-pictures|accessdate=2017-02-25|work=The Guardian|date=2017-02-17|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111215104/https://www.theguardian.com/world/gallery/2017/feb/17/aid-reaches-rohingya-refugees-in-bangladesh-in-pictures|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Inside Cox's Bazar: Rohingya refugees flee persecution in Burma, in pictures|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/11/17/rohingya-refugees-flee-coxs-bazar-pictures/aerial-view-sprawling-refugee-camp-balukhali-near-coxs-bazar/|accessdate=2017-12-09|work=The Telegraph|language=en|archive-date=2018-06-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180622150355/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2017/11/17/rohingya-refugees-flee-coxs-bazar-pictures/aerial-view-sprawling-refugee-camp-balukhali-near-coxs-bazar/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Starvation rife among Rohingya children in Bangladesh’s refugee camps|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/rohingya-crisis-latest-starvation-refugee-camps-balukhali-coxs-bazar-bangladesh-burmese-muslims-a8094741.html|accessdate=2017-12-09|work=The Independent|date=2017-12-06|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326085827/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/asia/rohingya-crisis-latest-starvation-refugee-camps-balukhali-coxs-bazar-bangladesh-burmese-muslims-a8094741.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[國際移民組織|國際移民組織]]把巴魯卡里和鄰近的[[庫圖帕朗難民營|庫圖帕朗難民營]]合稱為「庫圖帕隆－巴魯卡里聯合地點」（{{lang|en|Kutupalong–Balukhali expansion site}}）。<ref>{{cite web|title=Cox's Bazar: Kutupalong-Balukhali expansion sites Footpath and Access road as of 05 Dec 2017|url=https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/20171205_kutupalong-balukhali_expansion_sites_footpath_and_access_road_id0069.pdf|publisher=International Organization for Migration|accessdate=2017-12-21|language=en|archive-date=2017-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171222052301/https://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/20171205_kutupalong-balukhali_expansion_sites_footpath_and_access_road_id0069.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.npr.org/2019/04/05/709894267/rohingya-settle-in-for-the-long-haul-even-as-bangladesh-wants-refugees-to-go-hom|title=Rohingya Settle In For The Long Haul, Even As Bangladesh Wants Refugees To Go Home|last=Beaubien|first=Jason|date=2019-04-05|website=NPR.org|language=en|access-date=2019-04-06|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213200502/https://www.npr.org/2019/04/05/709894267/rohingya-settle-in-for-the-long-haul-even-as-bangladesh-wants-refugees-to-go-hom|dead-url=no}}</ref>2021年3月，難民營[[2021年3月羅興亞難民營大火|發生大火]]，導致人員傷亡，數萬人流離失所。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/3/23/bangladesh-probes-deadly-fire-at-rohingya-refugee-camp |title=Bangladesh probes deadly fire at Rohingya camp, 400 missing |publisher=Aljazeera |date=2021-03-23 |access-date=2021-03-24 |language=en |archive-date=2021-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324165118/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/2021/3/23/bangladesh-probes-deadly-fire-at-rohingya-refugee-camp |dead-url=no }}</ref>

